> mod (Activity module)  `forum`        `mod_forum`          `mod/forum/`
> 
> mod (Activity module)  `quiz`         `mod_quiz`           `mod/quiz/`
> 
> block (Side block)     `navigation`   `block_navigation`   `blocks/navigation/`
